EKIPIZZA - S01 E25: Džentlmenski sporazum
Pogledajte novu epizodu Mozzartove serije

07 Nov 2019

Natalija i Minja na šanku u Mozzartu gledaju talent šou, dok Gorana glasno negoduje jer bi pre gledala neku utakmicu. Kad Natalija i Minja dođu u sukob oko toga ko je od učesnika bolji, Gorana im nudi priliku da naprave džentlmenski sporazum…

EKIPIZZA - S01 E25: Gentleman's Agreement
Check out a new episode of the Mozzart series

07 Nov 2019

Natalia and Minya are watching a talent show at the bar in Mozzart, while Gorana is outraged because she would rather watch a match. When Natalia and Minya come into conflict over who is better than the participants, Gorana offers them the opportunity to make a gentleman's agreement ...
